<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>426</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>wǒ de jiǎo tà dìng le nǐ de lù 迦南426</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ de jiǎo tà dìng le nǐ de lù jìng, nǐ de líng yǐn dǎo wǒ xiàng qián xíng,
 lù shàng pù mǎn le zhǔ de ēn diǎn, zhǔ a wǒ xīn sū xǐng,
 lái rì duō zhǎng, qù rì duō yuǎn, wǒ rèn dìng nǐ de lù jìng,
 yǒu tǔ de jiù yào sā zhǒng, yǒu gāo shān jiù yào pān dēng, zhǔ a wǒ xīn sū xǐng.</lyrics>
</song>